| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2020-0265 — Mass File Rename (netwalker)"
| comment "Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: eda095ef-39b4-5399-bdb4-d68ed742c9b9"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
